{"md5":"aa616219e7014921b002ee367ead9eee","content":"\n\n<p>\n整理gcc下的attribute，避免遗忘。\n</p>\n\n<!--more-->\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-org7db5d3e\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org7db5d3e\">数据结构</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org7db5d3e\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org7d304a3\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"org7d304a3\">结构体非对齐</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-org7d304a3\">\n<p>\n在两个系统进行通信发送数据时，经常会要以结构体非对齐方式，以保证数据对应的情况下减小发送带宽。\n</p>\n\n<p>\n使用 <code>__packed</code> 来强制编译器不使用对齐。\n</p>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> __attribute__((__packed__))</span><br><span class=\"line\">{</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> cmd;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> data;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}cmd_normal;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\nLast Updated 2018-05-27 日 15:22.<br>Render by <a href=\"https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-renderer-org\">hexo-renderer-org</a> with <a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/\">Emacs</a> 25.3.1 (<a href=\"https://orgmode.org\">Org</a> mode 9.1.13)\n"}
